criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Female subjects;

          -  Persons aged between 20 and 59 years;

          -  Overweight or obese;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals consumed alcohol and / or chronic smokers;

          -  Individuals who do not have preserved cognitive status;

          -  Individuals users of multivitamins and mineral supplements, appetite suppressants and
             steroids;

          -  Pregnant women.
